  <h2 id="best-practices">Best practices</h2>

  <ul>
    <li><strong>Always use FormGroup</strong>: Wraps label + input for consistent spacing</li>
    <li><strong>Indicate required fields</strong>: Use <code class="inline-code">required</code> prop on Label and Input</li>
    <li><strong>Clear error messages</strong>: Explain why the error and how to fix it</li>
    <li><strong>Informative placeholders</strong>: Show examples of expected format</li>
    <li><strong>Relevant icons</strong>: Help visually identify the field type</li>
    <li><strong>Consistent variants</strong>: Use the same variant throughout the form</li>
    <li><strong>Group radios</strong>: Use <code class="inline-code">&lt;fieldset&gt;</code> and <code class="inline-code">&lt;legend&gt;</code></li>
    <li><strong>Progressive validation</strong>: Validate in real time or on submit depending on context</li>
  </ul>

